  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个健康科技系统的数据流图。核心是这个诊断引擎，它要同时对接EMR同步、患者记录、实验室分析，还要和HIPAA合规的数据仓库交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，诊断引擎是中心节点。我想确认一下流向：HIPAA仓库是只进不出，还是双向的？另外EMR同步是引擎主动拉取还是被动接收？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "HIPAA仓库是单向的，诊断引擎要把分析结果写进去，但引擎本身不直接读取仓库。EMR同步是引擎主动发起的，去拉患者历史数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那我这样布局：诊断引擎放中间，左边连HIPAA仓库用实线箭头表示写入，EMR同步、患者记录、实验室分析都放在右侧或下方，用箭头标明引擎主动拉取或推送的方向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "方向对了。不过患者记录和实验室分析这块，引擎是双向交互的——既读取也更新状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，患者记录和实验室分析都用双向箭头。现在检查整体结构：诊断引擎左侧输出到HIPAA仓库，右侧双向连接患者记录和实验室分析，还有EMR同步的单向拉取。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，EMR同步我再看了一下——其实是引擎被动接收推送，不是主动拉取。方向画反了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "收到，EMR同步改为指向诊断引擎的箭头，表示数据推送进来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "还有个小细节：HIPAA仓库那条线，我们内部规范要求用虚线或反向箭头表示\"归档写入\"，和普通数据流区分开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "反向箭头是指从HIPAA仓库指向引擎？但您之前说引擎写入仓库，这样会不会混淆？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "抱歉我表述不清。保持引擎指向仓库的方向，但用反向箭头符号（<---）来表示这是受控的归档通道，不是普通API调用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已完成最终调整：诊断引擎左侧用反向箭头连接HIPAA合规仓库，右侧接收EMR推送，双向连接患者记录和实验室分析。结构清晰了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
